                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-672-18550611 t18550611-672-punishment-76"></join>Five Years' Penal Servitude.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">There were three other charges against the prisoner.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Russell Gurney, Esq.</hi>
